Package pipeline

Class CartesianMatrixEvaluator

java.lang.Object
pipeline.CartesianMatrixEvaluator
Direct Known Subclasses:
TreeHandler
public class CartesianMatrixEvaluator extends Object
Provides utilities for evaluating Cartesian products over matrices. Includes support for computing sum and average of matrix values over coordinate pairs derived from set products.
